  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/49ae8e6e32a0338ecd503969e996f41c.poster.avif?t=1747906277\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/49ae8e6e32a0338ecd503969e996f41c.webm?t=1747906277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/49ae8e6e32a0338ecd503969e996f41c.mp4?t=1747906277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/00e8fbfa54379c1883a17b641bf7436f.avif?t=1747906277\" width=180 height=75 /></span><br><strong>Elynovia</strong>, a cursed land that was abandoned by god, once a peaceful place to live, now is nothing but eternal chaos and darkness. A place of the undead, demons, and unknown creatures roaming around aimlessly. The curse has not been lifted yet, until one day a god from another realm decides to interfere by reincarnation his greatest hero into this world. With the blessing of god, the hero's soul is able to choose and possess a new body or vessel from this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/383063b85c8232535f538f080ed21548.poster.avif?t=1747906277\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/383063b85c8232535f538f080ed21548.webm?t=1747906277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/383063b85c8232535f538f080ed21548.mp4?t=1747906277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979200/extras/8b1d74b207d87055355201f86bac06b4.avif?t=1747906277\" width=278 height=121 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully animated battles</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Both Enemies and Player have animated image</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Stunning and beautiful skill effect</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Monsters, Skills, and Items</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Over 50+ Monsters type</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Over 80+ unique skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Over 80+ unique items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-All playable creatures have a unique skill tree</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Element Affinity System</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each monster and player have different elements of weakness and strength</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random events, monsters, treasure, and traps on certain dungeon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle systems</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fast paced turn-based battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-No Random Encounter Enemies</p>",
